  wizard's POST /api/v1/settings/initialize and the Jellyfin auth bootstrap
  branch (server/routes/auth.ts). Default both to "unconfigured" on first
  install so the UI routes the operator to /setup (which sends serverType
  in the auth POST) instead of /login (which doesn't and would trip the
  ApiErrorCode.NoAdminUser throw at auth.ts:328). After the wizard
  completes, seerr writes initialized: true + mediaServerType: 2
